STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Derek KRIEGER, Defendant-Appellant. No. 18-0377 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed June 5, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A defendant appeals his convictions for third-degree burglary and two counts of criminal trespass. REVERSED AND REMANDED.

REVERSED AND REMANDED.
